messages.message:
Software Engineer Openings - Let's network?

Hi Brian, 

I wanted to reach out and see if you're interested in new roles? I have a few opportunities for Senior Software Developers for my clients in the Phoenix area that I wanted to see would be of interest to you. More importantly, I want to learn about what you're doing in your current role and what you look for in your next endeavor so that Apex can be an advocate for you and new opportunities! 

If you could, please give me a call at 480-368-2480 to discuss further. 

Thanks, 
Alex

Alexandra Lenar
480-368-2480 | alenar@apexsystemsinc.com
Thank you for your response! Since there are several different positions, it might be easier to discuss over the phone. Are you available this afternoon or evening?
